<!-- Company Story -->
<section class="section-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-intro">
      <h2>The Northway Story</h2>
      <p>For over two decades, Northway Construction has been the trusted name in commercial construction. What began as a commitment to quality craftsmanship and honest dealing has grown into a regional construction leader serving clients in Utah and Washington—without losing sight of what matters most: building relationships alongside buildings.</p>

      <p>We're not the biggest contractor, and that's by design. We're big enough to handle significant commercial projects with the resources and expertise they demand, yet small enough that you'll work directly with experienced leadership who take personal pride in every project. When you call Northway, you reach decision-makers, not layers of bureaucracy.</p>

      <p>Our approach is straightforward: listen to what clients need, provide honest budgets and realistic schedules, deliver quality construction through skilled trade partners, and stand behind our work. It's old school in the best sense—doing what you say you'll do, treating people fairly, and building things that last.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

