      <span class="section-label">Our Expertise</span>
      <h2>What We Build</h2>

      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Northway Construction specializes in commercial construction across multiple sectors. Our portfolio includes retail centers and stores, office buildings and corporate spaces, industrial facilities and warehouses, tenant improvements and build-outs, and commercial renovations. We handle projects ranging from 5,000 square feet to over 100,000 square feet—providing the flexibility that larger contractors can't match and the capability that smaller firms don't have.</p>

      <div style="margin-top: 3rem;">
        <h3>Service Areas</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.7;">We serve commercial construction clients throughout Utah from our Eagle Mountain office, with particular strength in the Salt Lake City metro area, Wasatch Front, Utah County, and surrounding communities. Our Washington office serves the Pacific Northwest market, providing the same quality and service throughout the Greater Seattle-Tacoma metro area and Washington state.</p>
      </div>
